form_north_german_confederation2_desc;이상적인 상황은 아니지만 국가 안보를 유지하고 북독일의 패권을 위해서는 북독일의 동맹국들에 접근해 연방을 결성해야 합니다. 단 하나의 깃발 아래, 단결된 전선으로, 우리가 성공하기를!;;The conditions may be less than ideal, but in order to maintain national security and strive towards North German hegemony, we must approach our North German allies and create a confederation. Only with a united front, under a single flag, may we succeed!;;;;;;;;;;;;;x,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;
