form_scandinavia_NEWS_LONG;북쪽 땅들이 스칸디나비아를 결성해 하나로 뭉쳤습니다. 수요일 오후 5시 스톡홀름의 주요 광장을 메운 금발머리 남성들과 여성들로 구성된 군중들이 새로운 정치적 상황에 대해 즉각적으로 그리고 정중하게 찬성의 목소리를 냈습니다. 경찰은 한 남성이 자신의 집 밖에서 ;스칸디나비아 만세'를 외친 뒤 무혐의로 풀려났다고 보고했습니다.;The lands of the north have come together to form the nation of Scandinavia. A reserved crowd of predominantly blonde men and women filled the main square in Stockholm on Wednesday at 5pm promptly and politely voiced their approval of the new political circumstance. Handshakes, respectful clapping and nods of approval were the order of the day as the evening progressed, with the city emptying by 9pm sharp as requested by authorities. Police reported that one man had been released without charge after shouting 멻urray for Scandinavia쬦outside his home.;;Die L쬦der des Nordens sind zusammengekommen um die Nation Skandinavien zu bilden. Eine zur쬦khaltende Menge 쬦erwiegend blonder M쬦ner und Frauen f쬦len den Hauptplatz in Stockholm p쬦ktlich am Mittwoch um Punkt 17:00 und stimmten den politischen Ver쬦derungen zu. H쬦desch쬦teln, respektvolles Klatschen und nickende Genehmigung waren die Order an dem Tag als zum Abend die Stadt sich leerte, wie von den Beh쬦den gefordert. Die Polizei berichtet das ein Mann ohne Anklage freigelassen wurde nachdem dieser Hurray f쬦 Scandinavien" ausserhalb seines Hauses gerufen hat.
